{
  "video_id": "C_eFjLZqXt8",
  "title": "Didier Sornette: How we can predict the next financial crisis",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 12818.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12818.0,
      "end_time": 14328.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14328.0,
      "end_time": 20979.0,
      "text": "we lived in an economy of financial growth and prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20979.0,
      "end_time": 24674.0,
      "text": "This was called the Great Moderation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24674.0,
      "end_time": 28080.0,
      "text": "the misguided belief by most economists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28080.0,
      "end_time": 31383.0,
      "text": "policymakers and central banks"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31383.0,
      "end_time": 34714.0,
      "text": "that we have transformed into a new world"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34714.0,
      "end_time": 38571.0,
      "text": "of never-ending growth and prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38571.0,
      "end_time": 43314.0,
      "text": "This was seen by robust and steady GDP growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43314.0,
      "end_time": 46314.0,
      "text": "by low and controlled inflation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46314.0,
      "end_time": 48553.0,
      "text": "by low unemployment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48553.0,
      "end_time": 52459.0,
      "text": "and controlled and low financial volatility."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52459.0,
      "end_time": 59091.0,
      "text": "But the Great Recession in 2007 and 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59091.0,
      "end_time": 62570.0,
      "text": "the great crash, broke this illusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62570.0,
      "end_time": 67594.0,
      "text": "A few hundred billion dollars of losses in the financial sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67594.0,
      "end_time": 71674.0,
      "text": "cascaded into five trillion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71674.0,
      "end_time": 73558.0,
      "text": "of losses in world GDP"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73558.0,
      "end_time": 77361.0,
      "text": "and almost $30 trillion losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77361.0,
      "end_time": 81306.0,
      "text": "in the global stock market."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81306.0,
      "end_time": 86501.0,
      "text": "So the understanding of this Great Recession"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86501.0,
      "end_time": 91862.0,
      "text": "was that this was completely surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 91862.0,
      "end_time": 93208.0,
      "text": "this came out of the blue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93208.0,
      "end_time": 96125.0,
      "text": "this was like the wrath of the gods."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96125.0,
      "end_time": 97916.0,
      "text": "There was no responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97916.0,
      "end_time": 99839.0,
      "text": "So, as a reflection of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99839.0,
      "end_time": 103448.0,
      "text": "we started the Financial Crisis Observatory."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103448.0,
      "end_time": 107386.0,
      "text": "We had the goal to diagnose in real time"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107386.0,
      "end_time": 109757.0,
      "text": "financial bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109757.0,
      "end_time": 115614.0,
      "text": "and identify in advance their critical time."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115614.0,
      "end_time": 118972.0,
      "text": "What is the underpinning, scientifically, of this financial observatory?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118972.0,
      "end_time": 123598.0,
      "text": "We developed a theory called &quot;dragon-kings.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123598.0,
      "end_time": 126804.0,
      "text": "Dragon-kings represent extreme events"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126804.0,
      "end_time": 130076.0,
      "text": "which are of a class of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130076.0,
      "end_time": 132919.0,
      "text": "They are special. They are outliers."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132919.0,
      "end_time": 136359.0,
      "text": "They are generated by specific mechanisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136359.0,
      "end_time": 139245.0,
      "text": "that may make them predictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139245.0,
      "end_time": 142143.0,
      "text": "perhaps controllable."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 142143.0,
      "end_time": 145970.0,
      "text": "Consider the financial price time series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 145970.0,
      "end_time": 148143.0,
      "text": "a given stock, your perfect stock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148143.0,
      "end_time": 150495.0,
      "text": "or a global index."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150495.0,
      "end_time": 152549.0,
      "text": "You have these up-and-downs."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 152549.0,
      "end_time": 156111.0,
      "text": "A very good measure of the risk of this financial market"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156111.0,
      "end_time": 158533.0,
      "text": "is the peaks-to-valleys that represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158533.0,
      "end_time": 160829.0,
      "text": "a worst case scenario"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 160829.0,
      "end_time": 164502.0,
      "text": "when you bought at the top and sold at the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164502.0,
      "end_time": 168251.0,
      "text": "You can look at the statistics, the frequency of the occurrence"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168251.0,
      "end_time": 170606.0,
      "text": "of peak-to-valleys of different sizes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170606.0,
      "end_time": 173157.0,
      "text": "which is represented in this graph."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173157.0,
      "end_time": 176189.0,
      "text": "Now, interestingly, 99 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 176189.0,
      "end_time": 179982.0,
      "text": "of the peak-to-valleys of different amplitudes"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 179982.0,
      "end_time": 183442.0,
      "text": "can be represented by a universal power law"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183442.0,
      "end_time": 186893.0,
      "text": "represented by this red line here."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186893.0,
      "end_time": 191039.0,
      "text": "More interestingly, there are outliers, there are exceptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191039.0,
      "end_time": 192942.0,
      "text": "which are above this red line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 192942.0,
      "end_time": 196701.0,
      "text": "occur 100 times more frequently, at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196701.0,
      "end_time": 200854.0,
      "text": "than the extrapolation would predict them to occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 200854.0,
      "end_time": 204791.0,
      "text": "based on the calibration of the 99 percent remaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204791.0,
      "end_time": 207040.0,
      "text": "peak-to-valleys."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207040.0,
      "end_time": 211640.0,
      "text": "They are due to trenchant dependancies"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 211640.0,
      "end_time": 215152.0,
      "text": "such that a loss is followed by a loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215152.0,
      "end_time": 218115.0,
      "text": "which is followed by a loss which is followed by a loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218115.0,
      "end_time": 221226.0,
      "text": "These kinds of dependencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 221226.0,
      "end_time": 226838.0,
      "text": "are largely missed by standard risk management tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226838.0,
      "end_time": 229767.0,
      "text": "which ignore them and see lizards"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229767.0,
      "end_time": 233586.0,
      "text": "when they should see dragon-kings."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233586.0,
      "end_time": 237503.0,
      "text": "The root mechanism of a dragon-king"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237503.0,
      "end_time": 240639.0,
      "text": "is a slow maturation towards instability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 240639.0,
      "end_time": 242261.0,
      "text": "which is the bubble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242261.0,
      "end_time": 244891.0,
      "text": "and the climax of the bubble is often the crash."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244891.0,
      "end_time": 248516.0,
      "text": "This is similar to the slow heating of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248516.0,
      "end_time": 251419.0,
      "text": "in this test tube reaching the boiling point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 251419.0,
      "end_time": 253909.0,
      "text": "where the instability of the water occurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 253909.0,
      "end_time": 257246.0,
      "text": "and you have the phase transition to vapor."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257245.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260922.99999999997,
      "text": "And this process, which is absolutely non-linear --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260923.0,
      "end_time": 263203.0,
      "text": "cannot be predicted by standard techniques --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 263203.0,
      "end_time": 267379.0,
      "text": "is the reflection of a collective emergent behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 267379.0,
      "end_time": 269758.0,
      "text": "which is fundamentally endogenous."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 269758.0,
      "end_time": 272971.0,
      "text": "So the cause of the crash, the cause of the crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272971.0,
      "end_time": 276155.0,
      "text": "has to be found in an inner instability of the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276155.0,
      "end_time": 282191.0,
      "text": "and any tiny perturbation will make this instability occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 282191.0,
      "end_time": 285891.0,
      "text": "Now, some of you may have come to the mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285891.0,
      "end_time": 288516.0,
      "text": "that is this not related to the black swan concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 288516.0,
      "end_time": 291451.0,
      "text": "you have heard about frequently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 291451.0,
      "end_time": 293868.0,
      "text": "Remember, black swan is this rare bird"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 293868.0,
      "end_time": 297277.0,
      "text": "that you see once and suddenly shattered your belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 297277.0,
      "end_time": 299751.0,
      "text": "that all swans should be white,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 299751.0,
      "end_time": 303295.0,
      "text": "so it has captured the idea of unpredictability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 303295.0,
      "end_time": 304804.0,
      "text": "unknowability, that the extreme events"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304804.0,
      "end_time": 307635.0,
      "text": "are fundamentally unknowable."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 307635.0,
      "end_time": 309360.0,
      "text": "Nothing can be further"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 309360.0,
      "end_time": 311998.0,
      "text": "from the dragon-king concept I propose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 311998.0,
      "end_time": 315716.0,
      "text": "which is exactly the opposite, that most extreme events"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 315716.0,
      "end_time": 318939.0,
      "text": "are actually knowable and predictable."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 318939.0,
      "end_time": 322444.0,
      "text": "So we can be empowered and take responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 322444.0,
      "end_time": 324663.0,
      "text": "and make predictions about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 324663.0,
      "end_time": 327863.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s have my dragon-king burn this black swan concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 327863.0,
      "end_time": 329489.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 329489.0,
      "end_time": 332429.0,
      "text": "There are many early warning signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 332429.0,
      "end_time": 334308.0,
      "text": "that are predicted by this theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334308.0,
      "end_time": 336675.0,
      "text": "Let me just focus on one of them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 336675.0,
      "end_time": 339827.0,
      "text": "the super-exponential growth with positive feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 339827.0,
      "end_time": 340987.0,
      "text": "What does it mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 340987.0,
      "end_time": 343160.0,
      "text": "Imagine you have an investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 343160.0,
      "end_time": 346314.0,
      "text": "that returns the first year five percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 346314.0,
      "end_time": 349469.0,
      "text": "the second year 10 percent, the third year 20 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 349469.0,
      "end_time": 352011.0,
      "text": "the next year 40 percent. Is that not marvelous?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 352011.0,
      "end_time": 355409.0,
      "text": "This is a super-exponential growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 355409.0,
      "end_time": 357346.0,
      "text": "A standard exponential growth corresponds"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 357346.0,
      "end_time": 361090.0,
      "text": "to a constant growth rate, let&#39;s say, of 10 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361090.0,
      "end_time": 364571.0,
      "text": "The point is that, many times during bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364571.0,
      "end_time": 368168.0,
      "text": "there are positive feedbacks which can be of many times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 368168.0,
      "end_time": 371867.0,
      "text": "such that previous growths enhance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371867.0,
      "end_time": 375355.0,
      "text": "push forward, increase the next growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 375355.0,
      "end_time": 377857.0,
      "text": "through this kind of super-exponential growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377857.0,
      "end_time": 380971.0,
      "text": "which is very trenchant, not sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 380971.0,
      "end_time": 384028.0,
      "text": "And the key idea is that the mathematical solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 384028.0,
      "end_time": 387666.0,
      "text": "of this class of models exhibit finite-time singularities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387666.0,
      "end_time": 391019.0,
      "text": "which means that there is a critical time"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 391019.0,
      "end_time": 394223.0,
      "text": "where the system will break, will change regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394223.0,
      "end_time": 397499.0,
      "text": "It may be a crash. It may be just a plateau, something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397499.0,
      "end_time": 399766.0,
      "text": "And the key idea is that the critical time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 399766.0,
      "end_time": 402295.0,
      "text": "the information about the critical time is contained"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402295.0,
      "end_time": 407779.0,
      "text": "in the early development of this super-exponential growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 407779.0,
      "end_time": 412139.0,
      "text": "We have applied this theory early on, that was our first success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 412139.0,
      "end_time": 415698.0,
      "text": "to the diagnostic of the rupture of key elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 415698.0,
      "end_time": 418227.0,
      "text": "on the iron rocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 418227.0,
      "end_time": 421049.0,
      "text": "Using acoustic emission, you know, this little noise"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 421049.0,
      "end_time": 423346.0,
      "text": "that you hear a structure emit, sing to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 423346.0,
      "end_time": 427037.0,
      "text": "when they are stressed, and reveal the damage going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 427037.0,
      "end_time": 429477.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a collective phenomenon of positive feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 429477.0,
      "end_time": 431174.0,
      "text": "the more damage gives the more damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 431174.0,
      "end_time": 433649.0,
      "text": "so you can actually predict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 433649.0,
      "end_time": 435789.0,
      "text": "within, of course, a probability band,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 435789.0,
      "end_time": 437702.0,
      "text": "when the rupture will occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 437702.0,
      "end_time": 440137.0,
      "text": "So this is now so successful that it is used"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 440137.0,
      "end_time": 444502.0,
      "text": "in the initial phase of [unclear] the flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 444502.0,
      "end_time": 447309.0,
      "text": "Perhaps more surprisingly, the same type of theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 447309.0,
      "end_time": 450037.0,
      "text": "applies to biology and medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 450037.0,
      "end_time": 453733.0,
      "text": "parturition, the act of giving birth, epileptic seizures."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 453733.0,
      "end_time": 457357.0,
      "text": "From seven months of pregnancy, a mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 457357.0,
      "end_time": 463021.0,
      "text": "starts to feel episodic precursory contractions of the uterus"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 463021.0,
      "end_time": 467125.0,
      "text": "that are the sign of these maturations"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 467125.0,
      "end_time": 470549.0,
      "text": "toward the instability, giving birth to the baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 470549.0,
      "end_time": 472920.0,
      "text": "the dragon-king."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 472920.0,
      "end_time": 475526.0,
      "text": "So if you measure the precursor signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 475526.0,
      "end_time": 481751.0,
      "text": "you can actually identify pre- and post-maturity problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 481751.0,
      "end_time": 483222.0,
      "text": "in advance."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 483222.0,
      "end_time": 486982.0,
      "text": "Epileptic seizures also come in a large variety of size,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 486982.0,
      "end_time": 490262.0,
      "text": "and when the brain goes to a super-critical state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 490262.0,
      "end_time": 493835.0,
      "text": "you have dragon-kings which have a degree of predictability"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 493835.0,
      "end_time": 499342.0,
      "text": "and this can help the patient to deal with this illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 499342.0,
      "end_time": 501527.0,
      "text": "We have applied this theory to many systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 501527.0,
      "end_time": 504382.0,
      "text": "landslides, glacier collapse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 504382.0,
      "end_time": 507949.0,
      "text": "even to the dynamics of prediction of success:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 507949.0,
      "end_time": 512335.0,
      "text": "blockbusters, YouTube videos, movies, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 512335.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515471.00000000006,
      "text": "But perhaps the most important application"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 515471.0,
      "end_time": 517837.0,
      "text": "is for finance, and this theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 517837.0,
      "end_time": 521276.0,
      "text": "illuminates, I believe, the deep reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 521275.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523971.99999999994,
      "text": "for the financial crisis that we have gone through."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 523972.0,
      "end_time": 528020.0,
      "text": "This is rooted in 30 years of history of bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 528020.0,
      "end_time": 531732.0,
      "text": "starting in 1980, with the global bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 531732.0,
      "end_time": 533819.0,
      "text": "crashing in 1987,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 533819.0,
      "end_time": 536188.0,
      "text": "followed by many other bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 536188.0,
      "end_time": 538900.0,
      "text": "The biggest one was the &quot;new economy&quot; Internet bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 538900.0,
      "end_time": 540825.0,
      "text": "in 2000, crashing in 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 540825.0,
      "end_time": 542873.0,
      "text": "the real estate bubbles in many countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 542873.0,
      "end_time": 545653.0,
      "text": "financial derivative bubbles everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 545653.0,
      "end_time": 547942.0,
      "text": "stock market bubbles also everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 547942.0,
      "end_time": 551893.0,
      "text": "commodity and all bubbles, debt and credit bubbles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 551893.0,
      "end_time": 554606.0,
      "text": "bubbles, bubbles, bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 554606.0,
      "end_time": 557245.0,
      "text": "We had a global bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 557245.0,
      "end_time": 561486.0,
      "text": "This is a measure of global overvaluation"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 561486.0,
      "end_time": 565508.0,
      "text": "of all markets, expressing what I call"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 565508.0,
      "end_time": 568677.0,
      "text": "an illusion of a perpetual money machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 568677.0,
      "end_time": 572629.0,
      "text": "that suddenly broke in 2007."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 572629.0,
      "end_time": 576863.0,
      "text": "The problem is that we see the same process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 576863.0,
      "end_time": 579594.0,
      "text": "in particular through quantitative easing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 579594.0,
      "end_time": 582778.0,
      "text": "of a thinking of a perpetual money machine nowadays"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582778.0,
      "end_time": 587181.0,
      "text": "to tackle the crisis since 2008 in the U.S., in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 587181.0,
      "end_time": 589469.0,
      "text": "in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589469.0,
      "end_time": 591859.0,
      "text": "This has very important implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 591859.0,
      "end_time": 595937.0,
      "text": "to understand the failure of quantitative easing"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 595937.0,
      "end_time": 597813.0,
      "text": "as well as austerity measures"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 597813.0,
      "end_time": 600622.0,
      "text": "as long as we don&#39;t attack the core,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 600622.0,
      "end_time": 605813.0,
      "text": "the structural cause of this perpetual money machine thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 605813.0,
      "end_time": 608429.0,
      "text": "Now, these are big claims."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 608429.0,
      "end_time": 611311.0,
      "text": "Why would you believe me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 611311.0,
      "end_time": 614191.0,
      "text": "Well, perhaps because, in the last 15 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 614191.0,
      "end_time": 617383.0,
      "text": "we have come out of our ivory tower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 617383.0,
      "end_time": 620119.0,
      "text": "and started to publish ex ante --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 620119.0,
      "end_time": 623447.0,
      "text": "and I stress the term ex ante, it means &quot;in advance&quot; —"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 623447.0,
      "end_time": 625585.0,
      "text": "before the crash confirmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 625585.0,
      "end_time": 628271.0,
      "text": "the existence of the bubble or the financial excesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 628271.0,
      "end_time": 631993.0,
      "text": "These are a few of the major bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 631993.0,
      "end_time": 636471.0,
      "text": "that we have lived through in recent history."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 636471.0,
      "end_time": 639311.0,
      "text": "Again, many interesting stories for each of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 639311.0,
      "end_time": 642025.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you just one or two stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 642025.0,
      "end_time": 644071.0,
      "text": "that deal with massive bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 644071.0,
      "end_time": 646407.0,
      "text": "We all know the Chinese miracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 646407.0,
      "end_time": 649477.0,
      "text": "This is the expression of the stock market"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 649477.0,
      "end_time": 652357.0,
      "text": "of a massive bubble, a factor of three,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 652357.0,
      "end_time": 654527.0,
      "text": "300 percent in just a few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 654527.0,
      "end_time": 657729.0,
      "text": "In September 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 657729.0,
      "end_time": 661376.0,
      "text": "I was invited as a keynote speaker of a macro hedge fund"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 661376.0,
      "end_time": 663825.0,
      "text": "management conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 663825.0,
      "end_time": 667880.0,
      "text": "and I showed to the conference a prediction"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 667880.0,
      "end_time": 672073.0,
      "text": "that by the end of 2007, this bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 672073.0,
      "end_time": 674042.0,
      "text": "would change regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 674042.0,
      "end_time": 677127.0,
      "text": "There might be a crash. Certainly not sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 677127.0,
      "end_time": 682369.0,
      "text": "Now, how do you believe the very smart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 682369.0,
      "end_time": 687799.0,
      "text": "very motivated, very informed macro hedge fund managers"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 687799.0,
      "end_time": 689755.0,
      "text": "reacted to this prediction?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 689755.0,
      "end_time": 691711.0,
      "text": "You know, they had made billions"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 691711.0,
      "end_time": 694546.0,
      "text": "just surfing this bubble until now."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 694546.0,
      "end_time": 696130.0,
      "text": "They told me, &quot;Didier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 696130.0,
      "end_time": 699167.0,
      "text": "yeah, the market might be overvalued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 699167.0,
      "end_time": 701063.0,
      "text": "but you forget something."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 701063.0,
      "end_time": 703415.0,
      "text": "There is the Beijing Olympic Games coming"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 703415.0,
      "end_time": 705679.0,
      "text": "in August 2008, and it&#39;s very clear that"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 705679.0,
      "end_time": 708871.0,
      "text": "the Chinese government is controlling the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 708871.0,
      "end_time": 710224.0,
      "text": "and doing what it takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 710224.0,
      "end_time": 714671.0,
      "text": "to also avoid any wave and control the stock market.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 714671.0,
      "end_time": 717142.0,
      "text": "Three weeks after my presentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 717142.0,
      "end_time": 719268.0,
      "text": "the markets lost 20 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 719268.0,
      "end_time": 721529.0,
      "text": "and went through a phase of volatility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 721529.0,
      "end_time": 724255.0,
      "text": "upheaval, and a total market loss of"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 724255.0,
      "end_time": 726523.0,
      "text": "70 percent until the end of the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 726523.0,
      "end_time": 729399.0,
      "text": "So how can we be so collectively wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 729399.0,
      "end_time": 733541.0,
      "text": "by misreading or ignoring the science"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 733541.0,
      "end_time": 736372.0,
      "text": "of the fact that when an instability has developed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 736372.0,
      "end_time": 738823.0,
      "text": "and the system is ripe, any perturbation"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 738823.0,
      "end_time": 742504.0,
      "text": "makes it essentially impossible to control?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 742504.0,
      "end_time": 747209.0,
      "text": "The Chinese market collapsed, but it rebounded."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 747209.0,
      "end_time": 751965.0,
      "text": "In 2009, we also identified that this new bubble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 751965.0,
      "end_time": 754551.0,
      "text": "a smaller one, was unsustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 754551.0,
      "end_time": 758183.0,
      "text": "so we published again a prediction, in advance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 758183.0,
      "end_time": 762510.0,
      "text": "stating that by August 2009, the market will correct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 762510.0,
      "end_time": 765191.0,
      "text": "will not continue on this track."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 765191.0,
      "end_time": 768343.0,
      "text": "Our critics, reading the prediction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 768343.0,
      "end_time": 772256.0,
      "text": "said, &quot;No, it&#39;s not possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 772256.0,
      "end_time": 773750.0,
      "text": "The Chinese government is there."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 773750.0,
      "end_time": 776432.0,
      "text": "They have learned their lesson. They will control."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 776432.0,
      "end_time": 778239.0,
      "text": "They want to benefit from the growth.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 778239.0,
      "end_time": 781895.0,
      "text": "Perhaps these critics have not learned their lesson previously."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 781895.0,
      "end_time": 785727.0,
      "text": "So the crisis did occur. The market corrected."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 785727.0,
      "end_time": 788063.0,
      "text": "The same critics then said, &quot;Ah, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 788063.0,
      "end_time": 789912.0,
      "text": "but you published your prediction."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 789912.0,
      "end_time": 791568.0,
      "text": "You influenced the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 791568.0,
      "end_time": 794701.0,
      "text": "It was not a prediction.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 794701.0,
      "end_time": 798058.0,
      "text": "Maybe I am very powerful then."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 798058.0,
      "end_time": 800102.0,
      "text": "Now, this is interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 800102.0,
      "end_time": 803039.0,
      "text": "It shows that it&#39;s essentially impossible until now"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 803039.0,
      "end_time": 805167.0,
      "text": "to develop a science of economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 805167.0,
      "end_time": 808310.0,
      "text": "because we are sentient beings who anticipate"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 808310.0,
      "end_time": 812373.0,
      "text": "and there is a problem of self-fulfilling prophesies."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 812373.0,
      "end_time": 816106.0,
      "text": "So we invented a new way of doing science."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 816106.0,
      "end_time": 818818.0,
      "text": "We created the Financial Bubble Experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 818818.0,
      "end_time": 821490.0,
      "text": "The idea is the following. We monitor the markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 821490.0,
      "end_time": 825658.0,
      "text": "We identify excesses, bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 825658.0,
      "end_time": 828962.0,
      "text": "We do our work. We write a report"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 828962.0,
      "end_time": 833234.0,
      "text": "in which we put our prediction of the critical time."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 833234.0,
      "end_time": 835809.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t release the report. It&#39;s kept secret."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 835809.0,
      "end_time": 838674.0,
      "text": "But with modern encrypting techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 838674.0,
      "end_time": 842696.0,
      "text": "we have a hash, we publish a public key,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 842696.0,
      "end_time": 846651.0,
      "text": "and six months later, we release the report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 846651.0,
      "end_time": 849050.0,
      "text": "and there is authentication."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 849050.0,
      "end_time": 853818.0,
      "text": "And all this is done on an international archive"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 853818.0,
      "end_time": 858018.0,
      "text": "so that we cannot be accused of just releasing the successes."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 858018.0,
      "end_time": 861410.0,
      "text": "Let me tease you with a very recent analysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 861410.0,
      "end_time": 864668.0,
      "text": "17th of May, 2013, just two weeks ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 864668.0,
      "end_time": 866346.0,
      "text": "we identified that the U.S. stock market"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 866346.0,
      "end_time": 868738.0,
      "text": "was on an unsustainable path"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 868738.0,
      "end_time": 872540.0,
      "text": "and we released this on our website on the 21st of May"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 872540.0,
      "end_time": 874585.0,
      "text": "that there will be a change of regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 874585.0,
      "end_time": 879369.0,
      "text": "The next day, the market started to change regime, course."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 879369.0,
      "end_time": 880860.0,
      "text": "This is not a crash."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 880860.0,
      "end_time": 883459.0,
      "text": "This is just the third or fourth act"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 883459.0,
      "end_time": 886322.0,
      "text": "of a massive bubble in the making."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 886322.0,
      "end_time": 889418.0,
      "text": "Scaling up the discussion at the size of the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 889418.0,
      "end_time": 890443.0,
      "text": "we see the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 890443.0,
      "end_time": 893364.0,
      "text": "Wherever we look, it&#39;s observable:"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 893364.0,
      "end_time": 896594.0,
      "text": "in the biosphere, in the atmosphere, in the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 896594.0,
      "end_time": 900498.0,
      "text": "showing these super-exponential trajectories"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 900498.0,
      "end_time": 903129.0,
      "text": "characterizing an unsustainable path"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 903129.0,
      "end_time": 905746.0,
      "text": "and announcing a phase transition."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 905746.0,
      "end_time": 907450.0,
      "text": "This diagram on the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 907450.0,
      "end_time": 910450.0,
      "text": "shows a very beautiful compilation of studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 910450.0,
      "end_time": 914160.0,
      "text": "suggesting indeed that there is a nonlinear -- possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 914160.0,
      "end_time": 918309.0,
      "text": "for a nonlinear transition just in the next few decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 918309.0,
      "end_time": 921931.0,
      "text": "So there are bubbles everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 921931.0,
      "end_time": 923895.0,
      "text": "From one side, this is exciting"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 923895.0,
      "end_time": 926655.0,
      "text": "for me, as a professor who chases bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 926655.0,
      "end_time": 931413.0,
      "text": "and slays dragons, as the media has sometimes called me."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 931413.0,
      "end_time": 934464.0,
      "text": "But can we really slay the dragons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 934464.0,
      "end_time": 936608.0,
      "text": "Very recently, with collaborators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 936608.0,
      "end_time": 939311.0,
      "text": "we studied a dynamical system"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 939311.0,
      "end_time": 942215.0,
      "text": "where you see the dragon-king as these big loops"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 942215.0,
      "end_time": 946136.0,
      "text": "and we were able to apply tiny perturbations at the right times"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 946136.0,
      "end_time": 951071.0,
      "text": "that removed, when control is on, these dragons."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 951071.0,
      "end_time": 954005.0,
      "text": "&quot;Gouverner, c&#39;est prévoir.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 954005.0,
      "end_time": 959799.0,
      "text": "Governing is the art of planning and predicting."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 959799.0,
      "end_time": 962552.0,
      "text": "But is it not the case that this is probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 962552.0,
      "end_time": 966452.0,
      "text": "one of the biggest gaps of mankind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 966452.0,
      "end_time": 969712.0,
      "text": "which has the responsibility to steer"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 969712.0,
      "end_time": 972428.0,
      "text": "our societies and our planet toward sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 972428.0,
      "end_time": 977272.0,
      "text": "in the face of growing challenges and crises?"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 977272.0,
      "end_time": 981767.0,
      "text": "But the dragon-king theory gives hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 981767.0,
      "end_time": 985335.0,
      "text": "We learn that most systems have pockets of predictability."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 985335.0,
      "end_time": 990235.0,
      "text": "It is possible to develop advance diagnostics of crises"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 990235.0,
      "end_time": 993794.0,
      "text": "so that we can be prepared, we can take measures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 993794.0,
      "end_time": 996549.0,
      "text": "we can take responsibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 996549.0,
      "end_time": 999296.0,
      "text": "and so that never again will"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 999296.0,
      "end_time": 1003150.0,
      "text": "extremes and crises like the Great Recession"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1003150.0,
      "end_time": 1007560.0,
      "text": "or the European crisis take us by surprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1007560.0,
      "end_time": 1009035.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1009030.0,
      "end_time": 1019030.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}